        "timestamp": "2019-04-23 20:57:01.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\n(2 comments)\n\nI think you can leave Drools applications don't need any changes doesn't do any OS packaging installs in its image.  It just does application level installation under non-admin account.\n\nOnce you fix the version, I think this may be ready to go, although I would prefer at some point the OS packaging stuff would move to a parent image and just leave application stuff under non-root policy account.   We don't need to tackle it right now.",
        "patchset_number": 1
